{"tid":503443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍戰機飛越對馬海峽訓練　稱「日本海不是日本的海」","createTime":"2017-12-19T00:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T11:18:51.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"abba7498aecd421a93f23cd1e3a8cca0668c15f5","tid":503443,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:29:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解放軍戰機飛越對馬海峽訓練　稱「日本海不是日本的海」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國解放軍空軍官方微博「空軍發布」今日發文，聲稱今日解放軍出動轟炸機、殲擊機、偵察機等在內戰機編隊，首度飛越對馬海峽遠赴日本海國際空域遠洋訓練，測試實戰能力，又表示「日本海不是日本的海」。<br />\n<br />\n「日本海不是日本的海，對馬海峽屬於非領海海峽。 依照《聯合國海洋法公約》，所有國家均享有航行和飛越的自由」文章中強調，有關訓練「合法、合理、合情」。<br />\n<br />\n文章引用空軍兩名「轟 - 6K」型號戰機機長講話，指「練兵備戰是新時代中國軍人必須全力以赴的主責、全神貫注的主業」，又稱自2015年起解放軍空軍開始每月進行多次遠洋訓練，形容是「愈飛愈遠，愈飛愈深，愈飛愈有底氣」。<br />\n<br />\n（澎湃新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171218/s00004/1513594990586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171218%2Fs00004%2F1513594990586&d=OOlVbkzSc%2FpoKpTIQIzIf5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ba8e21d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171218%2Fs00004%2F1513594990586&h=73eeed25\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171218/s00004/1513594990586</a>"},{"pid":"ed41e3f26001c9d69226d55d0fd7ebff2a284a6e","tid":503443,"uid":49247,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"南中國海呢？"},{"pid":"25507982e8fe631e6f62a87e2f002e6e46457553","tid":503443,"uid":116289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d386c74232b82493174e8ae2d371649e991bbc","tid":503443,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南中國海呢？</blockquote><br 